From: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Date: Sat, 6 Jan 2024 20:39:48 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 09/78] Platform/Sgi: enable autogeneration of iort table

Add the support to generate IORT table from the PCIe topology
information passed from the previous boot stage. This information cannot
be hardcoded as the previous boot stage generate it dynamically after
discovering the PCIe devices and setting up related IP blocks.

Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Change-Id: I5e73a5a3cbac3c91c1df647e514f9888ef3a4466
